{"lemma":"فُلان","slug":"فُلان","root":"ف.ل.ن","root_slug":"ف-ل-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-ل-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"فُلان","root":"فلن","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n34582"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D9%8F%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%86"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"A placeholder name for a person, used when a name is not known; a generic name; so-and-so","examples":[{"text":"يَـٰوَيۡلَتَىٰ لَيۡتَنِي لَمۡ أَتَّخِذۡ فُلَانًا خَلِيلࣰا","english":"Oh, woe to me! I wish I had not taken that one as a friend."}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare Classical Syriac ܦܠܢ (plān) and Hebrew פְּלוֹנִי (pəlônî)."},"ipa":["/fu.laːn/","/flɑn/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n34582","headword_ar":"فُلَانٌ","root":"fln","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"is a substitute for the proper name of a human being, (S, Msb, * K, TA,) i. e. of a male; (S, TA;) and in like manner ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnapu","text_ar":"فُلَانَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K, TA,) for that of a female; (TA,) each without"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al","text_ar":"ال"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb:) [the former may be rendered"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a man;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the latter,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a woman:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfulaAnu","text_ar":"الفُلَانُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfulaAnapu","text_ar":"الفُلَانَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"for other than a human being, (S, K, TA,) i. e. for a [particular] camel, (Lth, TA,) or for a [particular] beast, as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rakibotu AlfulaAna","text_ar":"رَكِبْتُ الفُلَانَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I rode such a beast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such a male beast"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Halabotu AlfulaAnapa","text_ar":"حَلَبْتُ الفُلَانَةَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I milked such a beast"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Msb, TA:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"has no dual nor pl.: (IB, TA:) [but] sometimes one says to a single person, mase.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaA fulu","text_ar":"يَا فُلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and to two,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaA fulaAni","text_ar":"يَا فُلَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and to a pl. number,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaAfuluwna","text_ar":"يَافُلُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and in the fem.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaA fulapu","text_ar":"يَا فُلَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; &c.; (K: [see more in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fl","text_ar":"فل"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) accord. to Kh,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuEaAlN","text_ar":"فُعَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and its dim. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulayonN","text_ar":"فُلَيْنٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or, as some say, it is of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulowaAnN","text_ar":"فُلْوَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"rejected, therefore its dim. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulay~aAnN","text_ar":"فُلَيَّانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulayowaAnN","text_ar":"فُلَيْوَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (T, L, TA;) like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_nosaAnN","text_ar":"اـنْسَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is [said by some to be]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_nosiyaAnN","text_ar":"اـنْسِيَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", of which the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"is rejected. and therefore its dim. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^unyosiyaAnN","text_ar":"اُنيْسِيَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T, L.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","K","TA","S","Lth","IB"]}]}}